Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.59,0:00:21.40,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.54,0:00:31.71,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.41,0:00:37.63,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.94,0:00:38.95,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.27,0:00:40.59,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.12,0:00:45.52,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.92,0:02:22.69,Default,SideM,0000,0000,0000,,That girl, Hatori Chise, \Nis officially dead in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.36,0:02:26.99,Default,SideM,0000,0000,0000,,So I chose a location \Nhere and plugged her in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.99,0:02:28.74,Default,Scarface,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Adolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.74,0:02:32.03,Default,SideM,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm glad you told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.52,0:02:34.68,Default,SideM,0000,0000,0000,,Sleigh Beggies are valuable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.43,0:02:38.17,Default,SideM,0000,0000,0000,,The ones with potential and ambition \Nare treasures, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.49,0:02:40.09,Default,SideM,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.76,0:02:42.79,Default,SideM,0000,0000,0000,,Go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.02,0:02:43.96,Default,Scarface,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.96,0:02:46.31,Default,SideM,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to drink with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.31,0:02:48.74,Default,Scarface,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Christmas gift from Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.53,0:02:52.43,Default,SideM,0000,0000,0000,,Just one shot, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.49,0:02:55.15,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,You got a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.88,0:02:56.95,Default,SideM,0000,0000,0000,,Tory.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.95,0:02:57.98,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.98,0:03:00.02,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,You both look terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.02,0:03:01.79,Default,Scarface,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't you come in here more quietly?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.04,0:03:04.22,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.22,0:03:06.74,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mind if I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.74,0:03:08.63,Default,Scarface,0000,0000,0000,,I never said you could touch that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.07,0:03:10.96,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,You still haven't fixed that arm of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.71,0:03:14.47,Default,SideM,0000,0000,0000,,Cartaphilus, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.47,0:03:15.96,Default,SideM,0000,0000,0000,,Have you had contact with him since?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.27,0:03:17.07,Default,Scarface,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.07,0:03:18.34,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.34,0:03:20.35,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,Hook me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.35,0:03:22.07,Default,SideM,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.07,0:03:24.46,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,A sorcerer that's been \Nwandering for centuries, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.67,0:03:27.34,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,Eternal life is a timeless theme.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.34,0:03:28.84,Default,Scarface,0000,0000,0000,,What a pathetic dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.84,0:03:30.43,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,You're so stuck-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.43,0:03:32.48,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,Brilliant, but you'll make\N enemies being like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:34.99,Default,Scarface,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need more than \Na few people on my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.63,0:03:37.73,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.18,0:03:39.50,Default,SideM,0000,0000,0000,,Tory, that's too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.50,0:03:42.50,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, just a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.50,0:03:43.98,Default,SideM,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.98,0:03:46.45,Default,Scarface,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.92,0:03:52.46,Default,Scarface,0000,0000,0000,,If I were brilliant, I wouldn't have \Nlet myself be threatened by him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.12,0:03:55.42,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.42,0:03:56.49,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,This is hilarious!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.49,0:04:00.16,Default,SideM,0000,0000,0000,,That's going to go on for another \Nfour hours, at least. Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.16,0:04:00.87,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.87,0:04:01.96,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,What a huge pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.18,0:04:03.56,Default,Scarface,0000,0000,0000,,Drink with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.88,0:04:04.94,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.94,0:04:06.68,Default,SideM,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tug on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.25,0:04:10.14,Default,Spongebob,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.14,0:04:13.89,Default,Spongebob,0000,0000,0000,,What is this, it's not just Adolf?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.25,0:04:15.42,Default,SideM,0000,0000,0000,,Merituuli.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.42,0:04:16.40,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,A fairy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:18.35,Default,SideM,0000,0000,0000,,He's my former master's familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.32,0:04:54.29,Magus-Internal/narrator,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,London...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.27,0:04:59.47,Magus-Internal/narrator,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,Weird, I don't feel groggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.80,0:05:01.23,Magus-Internal/narrator,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not coughing, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.22,0:05:04.49,Magus-Internal/narrator,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,I'm neither warm nor cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.81,0:05:14.91,Default,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.91,0:05:15.36,Magus-Internal/narrator,A certain YouTuber,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.52,0:05:20.59,Default,A certain YouTuber,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.62,0:05:22.91,Default,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,Cartaphilus.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.91,0:05:27.21,Default,A certain YouTuber,0000,0000,0000,,You know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.70,0:05:29.63,Default,A certain YouTuber,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.63,0:05:31.02,Default,A certain YouTuber,0000,0000,0000,,My name...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.02,0:05:33.15,Default,A certain YouTuber,0000,0000,0000,,Was my name Cartaphilus?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.55,0:05:39.55,Default,A certain YouTuber,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, I can see through you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.55,0:05:41.02,Default,A certain YouTuber,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.59,0:05:46.52,Default,A certain YouTuber,0000,0000,0000,,You need to go where you belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.56,0:05:48.23,Default,A certain YouTuber,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.23,0:05:54.85,Default,A certain YouTuber,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, it's just not right, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.21,0:05:56.12,Default,A certain YouTuber,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.98,0:06:09.25,Default,A certain YouTuber,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.25,0:06:10.67,Default,A certain YouTuber,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.34,0:06:12.55,Default,A certain YouTuber,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.55,0:06:15.95,Default,A certain YouTuber,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! Sorry! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.95,0:06:16.77,Default,A certain YouTuber,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.68,0:06:19.02,Default,A certain YouTuber,0000,0000,0000,,But, he...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.02,0:06:19.94,Default,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,Carta—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:22.28,Default,A certain YouTuber,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have such a cursed name!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.30,0:06:24.23,Default,A certain YouTuber,0000,0000,0000,,Cartaphilus...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.74,0:06:29.81,Default,A certain YouTuber,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:33.24,Default,A certain YouTuber,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Joseph.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:36.08,Default,A certain YouTuber,0000,0000,0000,,Help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.54,0:06:40.78,Default,A certain YouTuber,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me, Cartaphilus.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.99,0:06:45.64,Default,A certain YouTuber,0000,0000,0000,,What do we need to do to be saved?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.76,0:06:58.62,Default,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.83,0:07:02.79,Default,Blablador,0000,0000,0000,,Who'd you go to see?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.52,0:07:07.75,Default,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,It's him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.75,0:07:09.24,Default,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,Cartaphilus...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:11.45,Magus-Flashback,A certain YouTuber,0000,0000,0000,,Help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.35,0:07:14.74,Magus-Internal/narrator,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get his voice out of my ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.23,0:07:16.99,Default,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,How many days has it been now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.49,0:07:19.34,Default,Blablador,0000,0000,0000,,You've only been sleeping for two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.71,0:07:25.33,Default,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,So, why is Lindel-san's Selkie here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.13,0:07:28.53,Default,Strongbad,0000,0000,0000,,You're finally awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.38,0:07:31.30,Default,Arisu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.30,0:07:32.28,Default,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.28,0:07:33.09,Default,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.09,0:07:35.97,Default,Strongbad,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go let everyone know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.37,0:07:41.31,Default,Arisu,0000,0000,0000,,We've got a nasty situation... \NA pretty bad one, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.02,0:07:45.75,Default,Arisu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.03,0:07:48.69,Default,Arisu,0000,0000,0000,,Can I just pick out any outfit for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.69,0:07:50.53,Default,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.47,0:07:54.43,Default,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Alice, how old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.43,0:07:56.14,Default,Arisu,0000,0000,0000,,Eighteen this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.14,0:07:57.66,Default,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's fine, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.29,0:08:07.24,Default,Master Chief,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Chise.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.93,0:08:10.36,Default,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.36,0:08:11.54,Default,Master Chief,0000,0000,0000,,How do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.54,0:08:13.00,Default,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,Well, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.00,0:08:14.38,Default,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,How about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.38,0:08:15.73,Default,Master Chief,0000,0000,0000,,Well, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.26,0:08:20.25,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,I've never been able to get a good \Nlook at a living Sleigh Beggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.25,0:08:22.72,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad I got to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.72,0:08:24.59,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for being alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.59,0:08:25.97,Default,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.87,0:08:27.70,Default,Scarface,0000,0000,0000,,Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.58,0:08:36.25,Default,SideM,0000,0000,0000,,I hate to admit that he's my colleague, \Nbut sorry about my colleague.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.72,0:08:38.08,Default,SideM,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:40.33,Default,SideM,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Adolf Stroud.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.71,0:08:42.23,Default,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.22,0:08:45.66,Default,Scarface,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.10,0:08:47.50,Default,Scarface,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about my disrespectful\Nbehavior last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.72,0:08:50.45,Default,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.32,0:08:53.44,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Tory Innis.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.44,0:08:55.07,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,You can call me Tory.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.97,0:08:59.19,Default,SideM,0000,0000,0000,,We're from the college.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.19,0:09:00.34,Default,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,College?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.80,0:09:02.26,Default,SideM,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.63,0:09:06.66,Default,Master Chief,0000,0000,0000,,You can cut the small talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.13,0:09:09.93,Default,Master Chief,0000,0000,0000,,Can you get to business?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.13,0:09:16.41,Default,SideM,0000,0000,0000,,As we've already explained to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.41,0:09:20.49,Default,SideM,0000,0000,0000,,dragon hatchlings were poached \Nfrom the land of dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.38,0:09:23.29,Default,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,Two were taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:26.08,Default,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,The poacher left this behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.07,0:09:29.12,Default,Master Chief,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.12,0:09:31.36,Default,Scarface,0000,0000,0000,,It's a transportation device I made.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.08,0:09:36.06,Default,Scarface,0000,0000,0000,,Cartaphilus is likely behind this incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.11,0:09:40.28,Default,Scarface,0000,0000,0000,,He seems to have stolen the know-how \Nbehind the device when he took my arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.00,0:09:42.54,Default,Scarface,0000,0000,0000,,This is my failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.54,0:09:43.56,Default,Arisu,0000,0000,0000,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.94,0:09:46.12,Default,Master Chief,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.12,0:09:49.19,Default,Master Chief,0000,0000,0000,,I understand well that you \Ndidn't mean for this to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.88,0:09:56.74,Default,Master Chief,0000,0000,0000,,The question is why we need to join you \Nin finding Cartaphilus and the dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.26,0:10:02.99,Default,SideM,0000,0000,0000,,You have a friendship with the land of \Ndragons, and you're familiar with Cartaphilus.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.40,0:10:06.94,Default,Master Chief,0000,0000,0000,,Why is the college in the business \Nof looking for dragons, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.31,0:10:11.67,Default,Strongbad,0000,0000,0000,,Lindel-sama and the\Ncollege have an agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.67,0:10:13.23,Default,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,With Lindel-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.86,0:10:20.37,Default,SideM,0000,0000,0000,,Could you help us to bring the dragons \Nback to Lindel—to your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.37,0:10:23.70,Default,SideM,0000,0000,0000,,He's bound to that land. \NThis is for his sake, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.40,0:10:27.57,Default,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,Elias...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.57,0:10:28.64,Default,Master Chief,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.64,0:10:29.93,Default,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.20,0:10:32.87,Default,Master Chief,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't our business, and it's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.87,0:10:33.77,Default,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.77,0:10:37.37,Default,Master Chief,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten how fragile your body is?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.04,0:10:45.28,Default,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,I think you've forgotten, too, Elias.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.23,0:10:49.07,Default,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,It was also extremely \Npainful and agonizing,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.12,0:10:51.08,Default,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.08,0:10:53.02,Default,Scarface,0000,0000,0000,,That day?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.13,0:10:54.07,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,That day?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.18,0:10:55.55,Default,SideM,0000,0000,0000,,"That" day?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.83,0:11:00.07,Default,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, we're neither \Nobliged nor responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.97,0:11:05.90,Default,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,But unlike us, the dragons left the \Nland of dragons against their will.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.79,0:11:12.66,Default,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want those kids I played with
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.85,0:11:15.74,Default,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,to suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.37,0:11:24.72,Default,Master Chief,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.72,0:11:26.21,Default,Master Chief,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cooperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.44,0:11:29.80,Default,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.89,0:11:35.08,Magus-Internal/narrator,Scarface,0000,0000,0000,,Have you changed a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.80,0:11:38.97,Default,Master Chief,0000,0000,0000,,So, do we have any leads or ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.45,0:11:41.76,Default,SideM,0000,0000,0000,,None on where Cartaphilus might be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.23,0:11:46.17,Default,SideM,0000,0000,0000,,We have Lindel maintaining contact with \Nthe dragons, but things aren't very clear,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.17,0:11:49.35,Default,SideM,0000,0000,0000,,possibly because they \Naren't fully conscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.90,0:11:55.41,Default,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,I think Cartaphilus is in London.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.82,0:11:56.37,Default,SideM,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.27,0:12:00.24,Default,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's a hunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.43,0:12:05.98,Default,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,Stroud-san, do dragons \Nsell for a lot of money?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.98,0:12:06.52,Default,SideM,0000,0000,0000,,Ye—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.52,0:12:07.56,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,They sure do!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.56,0:12:08.95,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,A {\i1}lot{\i0} of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.52,0:12:12.75,Default,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.93,0:12:18.01,Default,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, can someone lend me a phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.05,0:12:21.83,Default,More SideM,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.65,0:12:25.29,Default,More SideM,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.29,0:12:26.29,Default,More SideM,0000,0000,0000,,How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.31,0:12:28.38,Default,More SideM,0000,0000,0000,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.79,0:12:29.57,Default,More SideM,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.96,0:12:31.98,Default,More SideM,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in Paris right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.85,0:12:37.71,Default,More SideM,0000,0000,0000,,Depending on price and terms,\N I may take on your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.35,0:12:41.36,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.36,0:12:43.64,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Pull it tighter!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.29,0:13:20.61,Default,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Seth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.61,0:13:23.03,Default,More SideM,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see, Chise-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.58,0:13:27.04,Default,More SideM,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and Mr. Ainsworth?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.57,0:13:32.03,Default,More SideM,0000,0000,0000,,I believe magic and sorcery are \Nnot allowed at the auction.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.62,0:13:37.12,Default,Master Chief,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I heard, so I'm using \Nneither magic nor sorcery.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.07,0:13:40.03,Default,Master Chief,0000,0000,0000,,I just reassembled the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.34,0:13:43.12,Magus-Internal/narrator,SideM,0000,0000,0000,,It's neither me nor Simon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.12,0:13:44.79,Magus-Internal/narrator,SideM,0000,0000,0000,,Who's face is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.05,0:13:49.48,Default,More SideM,0000,0000,0000,,I'll choose not to hear all your names.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.48,0:13:53.53,Default,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,Um, if it's possible, I'd \Nlike to contribute this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.53,0:13:55.59,Default,More SideM,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.82,0:13:56.96,Default,More SideM,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.35,0:13:59.95,Default,More SideM,0000,0000,0000,,We'll make this the first \Nitem of the afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.95,0:14:01.91,Default,More SideM,0000,0000,0000,,And then we'll move on to the main auction.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.43,0:14:03.57,Default,More SideM,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.88,0:14:04.60,Default,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.19,0:14:08.22,Default,More SideM,0000,0000,0000,,The dragon auction begins at 6 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.22,0:14:10.08,Default,More SideM,0000,0000,0000,,Until then, feel free to do as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.08,0:14:13.80,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,You sure do sell whatever you want here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.25,0:14:16.02,Default,More SideM,0000,0000,0000,,Chise-san, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.62,0:14:18.91,Default,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,A checkbook?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.23,0:14:20.54,Default,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,And a card.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:23.70,Default,More SideM,0000,0000,0000,,Half of the value of your sale \Nprice is deposited there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.70,0:14:24.92,Default,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,Half?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.20,0:14:28.00,Default,More SideM,0000,0000,0000,,You were both a product \Nas well as an exhibitor,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.00,0:14:29.42,Default,More SideM,0000,0000,0000,,so that's your share.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.88,0:14:31.92,Default,More SideM,0000,0000,0000,,Dragons are expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.92,0:14:35.18,Default,More SideM,0000,0000,0000,,Please use that if the college's \Nfunding is inadequate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.58,0:14:37.43,Default,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.86,0:14:40.12,Magus-Internal/narrator,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,Money, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.47,0:14:44.34,Magus-Internal/narrator,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, this money \Nreally belongs to Elias.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.92,0:14:48.61,Default,More SideM,0000,0000,0000,,You have a different aura about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.85,0:14:51.50,Default,More SideM,0000,0000,0000,,You've grown taller, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.50,0:14:53.22,Default,More SideM,0000,0000,0000,,You're different from when we last met.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.04,0:14:57.57,Default,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,I've changed in some ways, \Nand stayed the same in others.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.85,0:15:00.98,Default,More SideM,0000,0000,0000,,The most important parts \Nof a person seldom change.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.98,0:15:03.98,Default,More SideM,0000,0000,0000,,You're stubborn after all, \Nfor better or worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.21,0:15:07.12,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.12,0:15:08.36,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,What were you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.36,0:15:11.06,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, want to come to the college?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.05,0:15:14.67,Default,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone at home who \Ngets lonely when I'm not there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.62,0:15:19.48,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,Glad to see you're not easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.08,0:15:26.58,Default,Master Chief,0000,0000,0000,,If there's something you want \Nto say, say it out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.58,0:15:29.81,Default,Scarface,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't told her about \Nthe college, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.17,0:15:32.51,Default,Master Chief,0000,0000,0000,,She's not going to the college.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.51,0:15:34.54,Default,Master Chief,0000,0000,0000,,So there's no reason to tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.90,0:15:36.39,Default,Scarface,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do with the messenger?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.39,0:15:37.54,Default,Scarface,0000,0000,0000,,Did you destroy it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.56,0:15:43.54,Default,Master Chief,0000,0000,0000,,It's unlike you to be so fixated \Non a Sleigh Beggy, Renfred.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.76,0:15:46.69,Default,Scarface,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that I'm worried \Nabout a Sleigh Beggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.15,0:15:50.06,Default,Scarface,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried about the \Nfuture of a human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.33,0:15:51.68,Default,Scarface,0000,0000,0000,,She may be fine now,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.68,0:15:56.22,Default,Scarface,0000,0000,0000,,but how far is she going to grow if \Nshe's forced to be dependent on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.52,0:15:59.55,Default,Master Chief,0000,0000,0000,,Is that for us to discuss?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.61,0:16:05.98,Default,Master Chief,0000,0000,0000,,We find someone without direction, burden \Nthem with a chest full of knowledge,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.98,0:16:08.80,Default,Master Chief,0000,0000,0000,,and force them onto a ship that \Ntakes them into the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.35,0:16:13.73,Default,Master Chief,0000,0000,0000,,We act as if we've shown them a path, \Nand make them believe it's the only path.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.69,0:16:17.07,Default,Master Chief,0000,0000,0000,,The two of us aren't very different, are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.18,0:16:25.57,Default,Master Chief,0000,0000,0000,,Let me guess. You never wanted \Nto be a sorcerer, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.05,0:16:27.87,Default,Master Chief,0000,0000,0000,,Did someone force you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.06,0:16:33.69,Default,Scarface,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare choose my path for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.95,0:16:38.13,Default,Master Chief,0000,0000,0000,,That girl is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.91,0:16:41.22,Default,Master Chief,0000,0000,0000,,That's what Chise wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.68,0:16:47.45,Default,Scarface,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be interesting to \Nsee how long that lasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.88,0:16:52.25,Default,Scarface,0000,0000,0000,,Living creatures change, \Nwhether they desire it or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.01,0:16:58.99,Default,Arisu,0000,0000,0000,,A-Awkward, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.99,0:16:59.90,Default,SideM,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.90,0:17:03.31,Default,Arisu,0000,0000,0000,,That pile of bones doesn't get it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.17,0:17:07.11,Default,Arisu,0000,0000,0000,,There's a ton of people who \Ncan only tread their own path,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.11,0:17:10.91,Default,Arisu,0000,0000,0000,,even when they're shown rails to follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.31,0:17:14.75,Default,SideM,0000,0000,0000,,Do you tread your own path?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.95,0:17:19.26,Default,Arisu,0000,0000,0000,,The paths form where I choose to tread.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.95,0:17:24.05,Default,SideM,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice to be young.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.12,0:17:30.89,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,We hereby begin the six o'clock auction.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.89,0:17:35.35,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,The northern land of dragons is sealed off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.58,0:17:42.58,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,It was there that this purebred, \Nwinged dragon was raised!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.35,0:17:59.55,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Starting at 800,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.55,0:18:00.93,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,810,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.93,0:18:02.05,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,820,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.42,0:18:03.48,Default,C,0000,0000,0000,,850,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.72,0:18:04.64,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,900,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:05.44,Default,D,0000,0000,0000,,900,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.05,0:18:07.44,Default,C,0000,0000,0000,,920,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.44,0:18:08.44,Default,E,0000,0000,0000,,One million!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.24,0:18:16.76,Default,SideM,0000,0000,0000,,The college can manage up to 1.5 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.76,0:18:18.49,Default,SideM,0000,0000,0000,,If we go over...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.47,0:18:20.58,Default,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.28,0:18:22.16,Default,SideM,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the exhibitor?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.79,0:18:23.61,Default,More SideM,0000,0000,0000,,Him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.61,0:18:25.07,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,1,220,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.42,0:18:26.75,Default,SideM,0000,0000,0000,,A proxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.77,0:18:27.24,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,1,250,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.75,0:18:28.88,Default,SideM,0000,0000,0000,,Or a proxy for a proxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.88,0:18:30.48,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,1,250,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.48,0:18:32.11,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,1,250,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.66,0:18:40.64,Magus-Internal/narrator,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,That person's looking at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.64,0:18:42.02,Default,C,0000,0000,0000,,1,500,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.02,0:18:43.34,Default,C,0000,0000,0000,,1,500,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.34,0:18:44.96,Default,More SideM,0000,0000,0000,,How high shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.96,0:18:47.13,Default,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,As high as you know my balance goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.90,0:18:49.27,Default,More SideM,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.27,0:18:50.83,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,1,600,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.97,0:18:52.92,Magus-Internal/narrator,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,They're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.13,0:18:53.51,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,1,700,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.74,0:18:55.10,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.10,0:18:56.50,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Do we have anyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.08,0:18:58.91,Default,Lips,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.05,0:19:03.15,Default,Master Chief,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.52,0:19:04.32,Default,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.36,0:19:08.08,Magus-Internal/narrator,Lips,0000,0000,0000,,No one else can hear me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.08,0:19:09.49,Magus-Internal/narrator,Lips,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.26,0:19:12.33,Magus-Internal/narrator,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.12,0:19:16.07,Default,Lips,0000,0000,0000,,A woman that you could make use of.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.62,0:19:18.56,Default,Lips,0000,0000,0000,,Is that good enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.37,0:19:20.59,Magus-Internal/narrator,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,Use you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.59,0:19:22.11,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,1,800,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.15,0:19:23.17,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,1,800,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.90,0:19:25.30,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,1,850,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.38,0:19:26.74,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,1,850,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.84,0:19:28.27,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,1,910,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.36,0:19:29.95,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,1,910,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.95,0:19:31.13,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,1,930,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.17,0:19:32.68,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,1,930,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.68,0:19:34.21,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,1,970,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.21,0:19:37.19,Magus-Internal/narrator,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,Please do it if we're at our limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.52,0:19:39.85,Magus-Internal/narrator,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.41,0:19:42.93,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bad this is only \Na verbal agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.64,0:19:46.50,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't go home with any regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.50,0:19:47.82,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.31,0:19:49.53,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,2,600,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.93,0:19:56.96,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,2,900,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.96,0:19:58.61,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,2,900,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.90,0:20:03.33,Default,More SideM,0000,0000,0000,,This looks promising.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.03,0:20:14.62,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,2,900,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.62,0:20:16.07,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,We're at 2,900,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.07,0:20:18.82,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone for more than 2,900,000?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.24,0:21:09.87,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, that was reinforced \Nwith a specialized spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.87,0:21:11.00,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,How did it get out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.00,0:21:12.06,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.06,0:21:13.28,Default,B,0000,0000,0000,,We've never had this happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.44,0:21:20.58,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,It's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.58,0:21:22.04,Default,Scarface,0000,0000,0000,,...in its right mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.58,0:21:23.33,Default,Master Chief,0000,0000,0000,,Chise!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.43,0:21:36.19,Default,The Chief,0000,0000,0000,,He wants to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.26,0:21:41.84,Default,The Chief,0000,0000,0000,,He's scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.52,0:21:46.62,Default,The Chief,0000,0000,0000,,He's so miserable.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.69,0:21:54.84,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,You can hear the dragon's voice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.09,0:22:01.49,Default,Master Chief,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.49,0:22:03.27,Default,Master Chief,0000,0000,0000,,Those aren't your emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.02,0:22:05.76,Default,Master Chief,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to let them take you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.58,0:22:09.07,Default,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.78,0:24:00.11,Default,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,The dragon's sorrowful howls echo \Nthrough the skies of London.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.11,0:24:05.50,Default,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,The girl makes a decision to save the \Ndragon, but it was far too brutal.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.55,0:24:07.82,Default,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.82,0:24:09.33,Default,The Cheat,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home together.
